desc: A 501(c)3 charitable organization that provides resources and support to anyone impacted by mental health - directly or indirectly. Our mission is to raise awareness, promote understanding, and change the narrative surrounding mental health topics.

layout.text: “In honest and beautiful prose, Karena writes about confronting her struggles with bravery and courage, removing the stigma of mental illness and paving the way for others seeking empathy and acceptance.” —JEWEL, New York Times Bestseller, Never Broken, Musician, Songwriter
